{
  "lesson": "WC-01-02",
  "audioMaster": "training/module01-foundations/WC-01-02-full-narration-v1.0.mp3",
  "audioDurationS": 181.473,
  "method": "silencedetect -32dB/0.28s within known block windows; proportional fallback",
  "phrases": [
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p01",
      "text": "Every WashCentral screen carries the same tools in the top-right corner.",
      "startS": 0,
      "endS": 3.937,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p02",
      "text": "They follow you from page to page.",
      "startS": 4.347,
      "endS": 6.118,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p03",
      "text": "Three of them do the daily work:",
      "startS": 6.747,
      "endS": 8.304,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s01",
      "id": "p04",
      "text": "jumping anywhere, focusing the view, and asking questions in plain language.",
      "startS": 8.528,
      "endS": 12.88,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p05",
      "text": "Press Control K.",
      "startS": 13.3,
      "endS": 14.773,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p06",
      "text": "The command palette opens dead center, cursor already blinking.",
      "startS": 15.879,
      "endS": 19.899,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p07",
      "text": "It's the quickest way to any page.",
      "startS": 20.168,
      "endS": 22.116,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s02",
      "id": "p08",
      "text": "Rather than hunt through menus, you picture where you're headed and type it.",
      "startS": 22.417,
      "endS": 26.4,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p09",
      "text": "Now, the results.",
      "startS": 26.8,
      "endS": 27.739,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p10",
      "text": "Search reads the whole platform, not just page titles.",
      "startS": 27.739,
      "endS": 31.545,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p11",
      "text": "Each hit names where you'll land and the module it lives under,",
      "startS": 31.545,
      "endS": 35.533,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s03",
      "id": "p12",
      "text": "so the palette quietly teaches you the layout.",
      "startS": 35.533,
      "endS": 38.038,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p13",
      "text": "Watch the footer, then tap the arrow keys.",
      "startS": 38.5,
      "endS": 41.151,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p14",
      "text": "The highlight moves with each press.",
      "startS": 41.556,
      "endS": 45.826,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p15",
      "text": "The palette runs entirely from the keyboard:",
      "startS": 46.189,
      "endS": 47.035,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p16",
      "text": "arrows to move, Enter to open, Escape to back out.",
      "startS": 47.322,
      "endS": 49.549,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s04",
      "id": "p17",
      "text": "Build the habit early.",
      "startS": 49.972,
      "endS": 51.166,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p18",
      "text": "Press Escape.",
      "startS": 51.701,
      "endS": 52.398,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p19",
      "text": "The palette closes and drops you back exactly where you were,",
      "startS": 52.398,
      "endS": 56.807,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p20",
      "text": "without opening or changing a thing.",
      "startS": 56.807,
      "endS": 59.37,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s05",
      "id": "p21",
      "text": "Closing Search is always safe.",
      "startS": 59.37,
      "endS": 61.113,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p22",
      "text": "Now click the location selector.",
      "startS": 61.576,
      "endS": 63.406,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p23",
      "text": "By default it reads All Locations, your whole network.",
      "startS": 63.91,
      "endS": 67.532,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p24",
      "text": "This control decides which sites your dashboards and numbers come from.",
      "startS": 68.098,
      "endS": 71.878,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s06",
      "id": "p25",
      "text": "Right now, that's every wash you run.",
      "startS": 72.347,
      "endS": 74.612,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p26",
      "text": "Underneath, two lists.",
      "startS": 75.109,
      "endS": 76.162,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p27",
      "text": "One groups sites by state, with a count beside each.",
      "startS": 76.162,
      "endS": 80.152,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p28",
      "text": "The other drills into a single wash.",
      "startS": 80.152,
      "endS": 83.046,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p29",
      "text": "Pick either, and every dashboard narrows to match.",
      "startS": 83.046,
      "endS": 86.376,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p30",
      "text": "For support work, remember: it only changes your view.",
      "startS": 86.376,
      "endS": 90.102,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s07",
      "id": "p31",
      "text": "The data never moves, and one click back to All Locations restores the whole network.",
      "startS": 90.102,
      "endS": 95.367,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p32",
      "text": "Click the selector again to close it.",
      "startS": 95.889,
      "endS": 97.77,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p33",
      "text": "We browsed and picked nothing, so scope stays on the full network.",
      "startS": 98.836,
      "endS": 102.3,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s08",
      "id": "p34",
      "text": "Scanning the list never filters a thing until you actually choose.",
      "startS": 103.013,
      "endS": 106.852,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p35",
      "text": "Last tool.",
      "startS": 107.4,
      "endS": 108.116,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p36",
      "text": "Click Ask Shyne.",
      "startS": 108.116,
      "endS": 109.398,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p37",
      "text": "Shyne is the assistant built into WashCentral.",
      "startS": 109.398,
      "endS": 112.411,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p38",
      "text": "Ask it about customers, operations, or marketing in plain language,",
      "startS": 112.411,
      "endS": 116.242,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s09",
      "id": "p39",
      "text": "and it pulls the answer together.",
      "startS": 116.242,
      "endS": 118.39,
      "timing": "proportional"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p40",
      "text": "The Try Asking prompts give you a feel for its range.",
      "startS": 118.9,
      "endS": 121.945,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p41",
      "text": "Payment declines at one site, prepaid members gone quiet,",
      "startS": 122.715,
      "endS": 124.289,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p42",
      "text": "last week's damage claims, VIPs at risk of leaving.",
      "startS": 124.746,
      "endS": 126.358,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s10",
      "id": "p43",
      "text": "If that's a question you'd normally dig through reports for, try Shyne first.",
      "startS": 126.857,
      "endS": 135.6,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p44",
      "text": "At the bottom, a question box and a Send button.",
      "startS": 136.1,
      "endS": 138.904,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p45",
      "text": "Normally you'd type a question here and Shyne would answer.",
      "startS": 139.733,
      "endS": 142.544,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p46",
      "text": "We won't send one today.",
      "startS": 142.745,
      "endS": 143.941,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p47",
      "text": "What matters is the line just below:",
      "startS": 144.849,
      "endS": 147.047,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p48",
      "text": "the answer is AI-generated, so verify it before you act.",
      "startS": 147.307,
      "endS": 151.002,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s11",
      "id": "p49",
      "text": "Treat Shyne's reply as a fast first draft you always confirm.",
      "startS": 151.745,
      "endS": 155.414,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p50",
      "text": "Click Close.",
      "startS": 156,
      "endS": 156.981,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s12",
      "id": "p51",
      "text": "The window disappears with no question sent, your workspace right where you left it.",
      "startS": 157.612,
      "endS": 162.48,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p52",
      "text": "So that's the header.",
      "startS": 162.94,
      "endS": 164.103,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p53",
      "text": "From any screen, Control K jumps you anywhere,",
      "startS": 164.507,
      "endS": 167.525,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p54",
      "text": "the location selector focuses the view without touching a record,",
      "startS": 167.816,
      "endS": 170.993,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p55",
      "text": "and Ask Shyne answers your questions, as long as you verify first.",
      "startS": 171.282,
      "endS": 175.053,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p56",
      "text": "Three tools, one corner.",
      "startS": 175.473,
      "endS": 177.096,
      "timing": "silence"
    },
    {
      "block": "s13",
      "id": "p57",
      "text": "Learn them now, because every lesson ahead assumes you can reach them.",
      "startS": 177.413,
      "endS": 181.039,
      "timing": "silence"
    }
  ]
}